oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Harrison County Agricultural Society Job No. 38438
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm); Snow, Hank;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 3095) for an order placed by the Harrison County Agricultural Society for 100 two color window cards for a performance by Hank Snow at the Harrison County Fair in Corydon, Indiana on July 29. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
